7/ Can I mint a specific AI Moonbird?
No, the mint will be sequential. This approach made it possible to have ridiculously low mint gas fees! Assuming the gas price is 20 gwei, to mint:
3 AI Moonbirds - you will pay around $5 for the gas fee.
10 AI Moonbirds - around $12.

6/ Are AI Moonbirds connected with Moonbirds somehow?
Yes. For example, AI Moonbird #1234 will remind you of Moonbird #1234. However, AI Moonbirds are not affiliated with Moonbirds.

5/ Why did you create AI Moonbirds?
We think Moonbirds is one of the greatest NFT projects out there. The idea, style, and people inspired us! We love art and we love tech, so we created AI Moonbirds!

4/ So will I get full IP?
Considering what is written above in 3/, yes - you will get full intellectual property rights for the AI Moonbird you own.

3/ How do you create AI Moonbirds?
We use a neural network with diffusion models to create this art. This means that each AI Moonbird is a set of randomly mixed pixels, which after thousands of iterations ended up looking somewhat similar to the original moonbird.

2/ How many AI Moonbirds are available for mint and what is the price?
150 AI Moonbirds are reserved for creators. 9850 are available for mint.
The first 2500 are free. The remaining 7500 - 0.05 ETH each.
